,"tid":24852,"uid":55830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T19:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辛苦左五，六年。呢年開始自己好翻。</blockquote><br />\n咁咪好 由中二 到依家 我都有左六年了....."},{"pid":"f5038212eed747cd5ee2ce33eb0740bab143cb0d","tid":24852,"uid":25545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T19:56:06.000Z","msg":"細個有濕疹，之後斷過一排<br />\n而家又有返，好努力戒口<br />\n但情緒同壓力冇得控<br />\n成身R到一撻撻<br />\n好驚第時男朋友見到會介意<br />\n<br />\n其實有冇醫生可以介紹下<br />\n好想斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5666f9a8d17f91aa2a1bcacbaeae875d2d19d194","tid":24852,"uid":26658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T20:35:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>辛苦左五，六年。呢年開始自己好翻。</blockquote><br />\n咁咪好 由中二 到依家 我都有左六年了.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最緊要日日沖涼 以前打完波，冬天，懶 ，唔去沖涼，會令病情惡化。"},{"pid":"06a5ae77f7afd8255bf7660ca2c4790e800a0d9d","tid":24852,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T21:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>辛苦左五，六年。呢年開始自己好翻。</blockquote><br />\n咁咪好 由中二 到依家 我都有左六年了.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最緊要日日沖涼 以前打完波，冬天，懶 ，唔去沖涼，會令病情惡化。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最緊要保持個人衞生啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacd9f48a509f6b1f57ec81007a12289f90b604f","tid":24852,"uid":37070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T22:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84945796b62228f7dbd6caba1b02f98c862139ce","tid":24852,"uid":48039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T22:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>過來人講兩句心得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1) 飲多啲水，唔好淨係飲飲品，多化學野未必好。始終香港秋冬乾，所以一定要飲好多水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 做多啲運動，出下汗。但係千祈唔好搲，用毛巾印走啲汗 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3) 保持心境開朗，屌我知講就易，但係我覺得都幾重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4) 最難做到，就係離開致敏源 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企執乾淨啲，唔好留啲塵啊喺間房。蝦，海鮮嗰啲少食。空氣方面就冇得救架啦，移民啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有乾嘅話記住搽野，以前搽過一隻 AI Cream，幾貴下，但係好好效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學生哥冇乜多餘錢買 between幾錢左右 依家用左幾年100蚊一盒有類固醇既藥膏</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪撚搽類固醇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n支野可能百幾掛，我都唔肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇試過一支野叫cetaphil restoring cream 咁上下啦<br />\n唔多記得 兩百幾一支 屈臣&prime;屎&prime;有 唔識打<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好用 可以試下 以前啲cream渣年幾就要轉<br />\n依支一茶茶左幾年都覺得仲係work"},{"pid":"2c3e611df46f79af22d0373e4eff7da364714fb4","tid":24852,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T22:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港濕疹極嚴重 呢加唔係香港住咩事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係，我覺得係空氣污染問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1011f05ace0e087bc208a9411a8a143a1f13d6","tid":24852,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:13:06.000Z","msg":"搽Vaseline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生係眉對下眼皮位 好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090a49c4fecdd221504767713d9b9899f3c033e0","tid":24852,"uid":2321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搽Vaseline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 生係眉對下眼皮位 好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成面都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你呢個位我間中會有"}]}